      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "JAKEY BLUE (3) filled a minor placing last start at this track behind Laurie's Ferrari (19.60) in a Grade 3/4. Has the early speed to land on the pace and can stick on. Didn't win last time but still ran one of the quickest times on the card. Top chance in this line up. PANDA UNLEASHED (1) was an impressive winner last time in quickest of the meeting when scoring by half a length (30.61) at this track. Looks a primary danger. SWIFT BONNIE (2) turned in a plain effort last time when sixth at this track over 431m behind My Irish (25.60) in a Grade 5. Cannot be underestimated. WALTER WANTED (6) is worth a look despite no experience at this trip.",
